Now add the two base 10 results together:
\[ 33496 + 31845 = 65341_{10} \]

Finally, convert the sum \(65341_{10}\) back to base 11:
\[ 65341_{10} = 3 \cdot 11^4 + 6 \cdot 11^3 + 10 \cdot 11^2 + 10 \cdot 11^1 + 0 \cdot 11^0 \]
